    <h1>Desktop Shortcut Installer</h1>
    <p>This installer will help you create a desktop shortcut to quickly access the Grabovoi Ritual Calendar application.</p>

    <h2>How to Install the Desktop Shortcut</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Download the shortcut installer file from the link below.</li>
      <li>Run the installer and follow the on-screen instructions.</li>
      <li>The shortcut will be placed on your desktop for easy access.</li>
      <li>Double-click the shortcut anytime to open the application.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Download Installer</h2>
    <p><a href="installer.exe" download>Grabovoi Calendar Desktop Shortcut Installer</a></p>

    <h2>Manual Shortcut Creation</h2>
    <p>If you prefer, you can create the shortcut manually:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Right-click on your desktop, select <code>New &gt; Shortcut</code>.</li>
      <li>Enter the URL of the app: <code>https://fairefaretravels.github.io/10k/</code></li>
      <li>Name the shortcut <strong>Grabovoi Calendar</strong>.</li>
      <li>Click <code>Finish</code>.</li>
    </ul>

